WEBVTT

1
01:54:49.130 --> 01:54:50.710 
这根本不是雷暴
This is no thunderstorm.

2
01:54:51.250 --> 01:54:53.630 
这是场战争!
It's a thunder-battle!

3
01:54:54.590 --> 01:54:55.590 
看!
Look!

4
01:55:00.640 --> 01:55:02.600 
天啊
Well, bless me.

5
01:55:02.850 --> 01:55:04.560 
传说是真的
The legends are true.

6
01:55:04.810 --> 01:55:08.730 
巨人! 石巨人!
Giants! Stone-Giants!

7
01:55:15.860 --> 01:55:16.700 
躲好 傻瓜!
Take cover, you fool!

8
01:55:18.780 --> 01:55:20.490 
抓紧!
Hold on!

